title: ADB, Japan Extend $2 Million For Education, Health Services (ADB - Asian Development Bank)
text: ( Source : ADB - Asian Development Bank ) ULAANBAATAR, MONGOLIA - The Asian Development Bank (ADB) and the Ministry of Finance signed today two technical assistance grant agreements for $2 million to help Mongolia increase access to health
